channel.title: Go Baby Go Seattle
channel.description:
Hi Go Baby Go teams!
Go Baby Go Seattle is led by Dr. Heather Feldner, a pediatric physical therapist and postdoctoral researcher in the University of Washington Department of Mechanical Engineering, and Dr. Shawn Israel, also a pediatric physical therapist at Waypoint Pediatric Therapies (Issaquah, WA) and a teaching associate in the University of Washington Department of Rehabilitation Medicine.
We are so excited to be a part of the GBG Connect community!
Please visit our [Facebook page](https://www.facebook.com/GBGSeattle/), and for more information about car workshops, outreach, and research, email us at gobabygoseattle@gmail.com
